 (1) Na7 bo5 siu7 tioh8 Seng3 Sin5, sui-bong2 lan2 it-seng lai5 te3 Chu2 Ia5-sou, iah8 si7 boe7-oe7 liau2-kai2 I e5 ui2-toa7 kap Sin5-seng3. Tui3 I e5 hak8-seng e5 keng-giam7 lan2 thang chai. Ia5-sou chio hak8-seng, tui3 ke7 e5 sou2-chai7 ka7 in seng-koan5, tui3 liah8 hi5 seng kau3 liah8 lang5 e5 sou2-chai7. In kap I saN-kap toa3 saN-ni5 ku2. Ti7 chit-e5 tiong-kan in choe3 ko-siong7 e5 kang, chiu7-si7 thoan5 chin2-kiu3 e5 hok-im hou7 ban7-bin5. Chong2-si7 Ia5-sou siu7 si2 tai5 loh8 thou5 e5 si5, in e5 ng3-bang7 kap i saN-kap tai5 ti7 bong7-lai7. Hak8-seng si3-soaN3 koh-chai3 to3-khi3 pun2 sou2-chai7 koh choe3 ku7 thau5-lou7. In long2 siuN7 Ia5-sou i2-keng si2 lah; m7-ku2 I tui3 si2 koh-oah8, ti7 kui2-na7 sou2-chai7 chhut-hian7 hou7 in khoaN3-kiN3. U7 chit8 pai2 I chhut-hian7 ti7 Ka-li7-li7 e5 hai2-piN, hou7 Pi2-tek khoaN3-kiN3, i sui5-si5 jin7-tioh8 si7 Chu2 Ia5-sou; chong2-si7 ui7-tioh8 kian3-siau3, soa3 thiau3 loh8 chui2, lai5 bih, m7-kaN2 khi2-lai5 kiN3 Chu2. In-ui7 u7 nng7-hang7 e5 in-toaN ti7-teh, thau5 chit8-hang7 chiu7-si7 tui3 i m7-jin7 Ia5-sou i2-lai5 thau5 chit8 pai2 khoaN3-kiN3 Ia5-sou, in-ui7 i kong2 na7-si7 tioh8 pang3-sak siN3-mia7 iah8 beh te3 Ia5-sou, tek-khak bo5 kong2 m7-bat I, chong2-si7 sit8-chai7 I u7 m7-jin7 Ia5-sou. Sou2-i2 chin kian3-siau3 beh thai2 oe7 kham-tit lai5 khia7 ti7 Chu2 e5 bin7-cheng5¡K? Te7-ji7 hang7 chiu7-si7, kian3-siau3 kau3 boe7 kong2 tit, in-ui7 ti7 saN-ni5 cheng5 kap tang5-phoaN7 iu5-goan5 ti7 chit-e5 sou2-chai7 siu7 tiau3 lai5 choe3 I e5 hak8-seng, teh choe3 ko-siong7 e5 kang, chiu7-si7 in2-chhoa7 lang5 lai5 kui Chu2; hian7-si5 eng-kai tioh8 soa3-chiap hit-e5 kang chiah tioh8; m7-ku2, koh to3-lai5 pun2 sou2-chai7, chit-tiap8 koh teh choe3 ku7 thau5-lou7. Sou2-i2 m7-kaN2 khi2-lai5 kiN3 Chu2. Chong2-si7 Ia5-sou tui3 si2 koh-oah8 e5 si5, in sou2 sit-loh8 e5 ng3-bang7 iah8 koh-oah8. Koh tui3 siu7 Seng3 Sin5 chhiong-moa2 e5 si5, in chiu7 bat Ia5-sou chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3, tui3 hit-tiap8 liau2-au7, sui-bong2 siu7 khun2-tiok8 kap ham7-hai7, ia7 si7 bo5 iau3-kin2, choan-sim thoan5 hok-im lai5 chin7 in siu7 tiau3 e5 kang. 
 (2) Hian7-si5 e5 se3-tai7 u7 chin-choe7 lang5 lai5 teh te3 Ia5-sou, chong2-si7 bo5 tit-tioh8 I e5 khui3-lat8 kap keng-giam7 I e5 Sin5-seng3--e5 iau2 chin-choe7. Sou2-i2 chit khoan2 e5 lang5 khoai3 siu7 be5-hek8. In kan-ta siuN7 kong2 Ia5-sou si7 chit8 e5 oan5-choan5 e5 lang5, ia7 ti7 kui2-na7 se3-ki2 cheng5 i2-keng si2-khi3 lah! Chong2-si7 tui3 hiah-e5 hoan2-hoe2 koe2-piN3 kap ki5-to2 e5 lang5, tu2 chhin-chhiuN7 Po2-lo5 u7 tit-tioh8 Chu2 e5 lat8, iah8 Chu2 u7 eng7 I e5 eng5-kng teh hian2-beng5 I pun2-sin ti7 in e5 tiong-kan. 
